Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.54,0:00:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people\Nseek the answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future --\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.54,0:00:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright,\Nbut I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.54,0:00:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.15,0:00:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.99,0:01:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.14,0:01:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.44,0:01:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.58,0:01:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really\Nneed everything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.59,0:01:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.07,0:02:00.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Rainbase"                 "Alubarna"\N      "Yuba" "Erumalu" "Nanohana" "Katorea"\N"Spiders Caf√©"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.04,0:01:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years have passed\Nsince a single drop of rain fell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.71,0:01:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the kingdom of oases.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.98,0:02:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing hope beyond turmoil,\Nthe people take up weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.65,0:02:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having escaped from the trap at\NRaindinners, Luffy and the others
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.79,0:02:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,set out toward Alubarna to plead with\Na rebel army that numbered two million,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.99,0:02:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he was caught by a waiting\NCrocodile, and they began a duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.00,0:02:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, unable to do\Nanything in the face
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.67,0:02:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of his overwhelming power,\NLuffy fell before him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.68,0:02:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will this situation continue to\Ndeteriorate into a worst-case scenario?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dash For a Miracle!\NAlabasta Animal Land"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! T-There's so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The water...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The water is coming forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I say so, Luffy-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This land is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.68,0:03:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuba still lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.69,0:03:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuba is going to die from\Nthat one, final sandstorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, the flame of anger in\Nthe rebel army will burn even hotter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This outdated consideration for others
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is going to destroy this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the same goes for you,\NStraw Hat Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had abandoned\Nyour worthless feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you would have lived longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt you still feel\Nindebted to this water, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, you're still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like that hurts. But you'll\Nbe out of your misery soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a waste of my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.66,0:05:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No big deal. Once we get\Nthrough this sand, it will rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like always.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep coming! Keep coming as\Noften as you want, sandstorms!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuba will never give in to the sand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, that's when it happened!\NThat's when I said to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You bowlegged bastard!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when it started. Ever since,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the crabs of the world have been\Nbothered about being bowlegged.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.64,0:06:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why they walk sideways, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh. Incidentally, at the time,\Nthere was something
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.98,0:06:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,jumping up and down\Nbehind him. It was a lobster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.32,0:06:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So lobsters-- they're crabs, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.32,0:06:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they're crabs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.99,0:06:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro, you're just wasting your\Nenergy doing that, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave him alone, Nami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If those guys aren't doing something,\Nthey can't keep focused.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not that adept. Especially...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that muscle freak, now that\Nhe's had a taste of the level
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Seven Warlords have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.62,0:07:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you, what are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and spell it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you want me to say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're scared. You're worried\Nthat maybe Luffy might lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who, me?! Scared, you say?! Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.97,0:07:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Fancy eyebrows!\N--That does it! Now I'm mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... moss head!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna go at it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out! This is pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.98,0:07:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are who they are.\NEveryone's a bit worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.99,0:07:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time for me,\Nthe vice-captain, to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it easy, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san won't lose. I mean,\Nwe promised him, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That we'd be waiting for him in Alubarna?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem more worried\Nthan any of us, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.34,0:08:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ow!\N--You should just worry about the rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that, Vivi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.94,0:08:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have to cover for us, we're done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then, switch your\Nminds over to "Alubarna"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.62,0:08:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Pincers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's that?\N--A name for the crab.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pincers," you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No good?\N--Nothing wrong with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, go to Alubarna?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.64,0:08:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're chasing after the\NStraw Hat pirates, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or are we reinforcing the royal army?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.31,0:08:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You decide what to do when you're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean that!\NExactly what is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.65,0:08:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just follow your sense of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.99,0:08:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever happens, I'll accept responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.33,0:08:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Smoker, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:09:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something sudden came up.\NI'm heading out to sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be prepared to receive communication\Nfrom me at any time, Tashigi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep a close watch on\Nwhere this country ends up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it falls, or whether it survives,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,something is sure to happen\Nto mark the start of a new age.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant... Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep a close watch on\Nwhere this country ends up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it falls, or whether it survives,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,something is sure to happen\Nto mark the start of a new age.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going after the pirate\NStraw Hat Luffy, and everyone under him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All hands, reinforce your gear!\NPrepare to depart for Alubarna!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:10:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! We can't cross\Nthe river with this crab?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moving Crabs are creatures of the desert,\Nso they don't take to water.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a crab, right? A crab!\NNot a lobster! Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is a problem. Not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we just blithely swim across\Nthis river, as wide as a sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're not going to\Nmake it in time! And look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After we cross the river, there's\Nstill dozens of kilos worth of desert!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this crab can't get to the other shore,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are we supposed to run from there on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we'll make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's absolutely impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh. Hey, the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I can see Sandora River!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do something, Pincers-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Pincers loves dancing girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Will this do?\N--Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.32,0:11:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, he's looking this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.66,0:11:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're accelerating!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.33,0:11:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've now messed up two\Nanimals with all this nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, pervy power!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what has this solved? Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.35,0:11:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.69,0:11:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now, this crab is incredible!\NI don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a miracle!\NJust stay on the water, and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, run, run all the way! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.37,0:11:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can make it! Keep going!\NYou can do it! This crab can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's this?! Am I imagining\Nthings, or are we sinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.37,0:11:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are sinking, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop sinking, you crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No time to whine about it.\NKeep moving forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't there any boats?\NHow many kilos to the other shore?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About 50 kilos.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.99,0:12:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who can swim that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Pincers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.33,0:12:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be\Ncasually waving goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.03,0:12:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a rare Sandoran catfish!\NThey're only very rarely seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.03,0:12:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to explain that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:12:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, humans are their favorite food!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.70,0:13:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might tell us that first!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let go! I can't see anything\Nin front of me, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper, let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.99,0:13:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kung Fu Dugongs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say they won't\Nneglect their senior pupil.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.00,0:13:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not like we're\NLuffy's pupils, or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.34,0:13:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, they saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, just a little\Nfarther! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.34,0:13:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.35,0:13:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things have been going smoothly.\NCan we make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.02,0:13:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a tough one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even riding on Lashes-kun,\NI'm not sure there's enough time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.02,0:13:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's more, he could\Nonly carry, uh... two of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.36,0:13:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if Baroque Works is going to\Nattack us, it will be from here on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.03,0:13:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there any way for\Nall of us to act together?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.97,0:14:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, there isn't any, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, is it the enemy?\NA-A-Are they here already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.66,0:14:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Supersonic Duck Squadron!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've come to get us, haven't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a difference in the level\Nof pirate that you and I are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuba is going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, the flame of anger in\Nthe rebel army will burn even hotter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.97,0:16:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, who have the name of "D"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"D"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.99,0:16:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.99,0:16:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, that was\Na pointless question, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:16:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Vivi-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.68,0:17:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I've got a handle on your ability,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.95,0:17:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this won't turn out like last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overexert yourself.\NYou must be seriously hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This works out perfectly.\NWhy don't you save that boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is a courageous knight
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who delivered your precious\Nprincess to this land, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.98,0:17:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, the princess is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.98,0:17:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's on her way to Alubarna right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.98,0:17:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure about what will\Nhappen to her later, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.32,0:17:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation is what it is, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm no match for her, then just\Nwho will be able to protect Vivi-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait, Cobra.\NWe're going to defend Alabasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.63,0:18:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not about to turn it over to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:34.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Royal Army" "Rebel Army"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.64,0:18:40.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"The capital, Alubarna"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Look lively!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.65,0:18:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stack it up higher!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.65,0:18:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready cannons at the southern gate!\NStop dawdling around! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.99,0:18:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring more cannonballs over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaka-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.33,0:19:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy's number is said\Nto be well over two million!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of\NHis Highness's attack on Nanohana?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have served him for\Nten years, so I was quite...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.94,0:19:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. There's really no way\Nanyone could believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only presume that something\Nmust have happened to the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if so, it's all the more reason\Nwhy we must not lose this fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not flinch at the enemy's number.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.09,0:19:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the King's sake, as well as for that\Nof Vivi-sama, who has returned home,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we are going to defend this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who is not\Ninvolved in this battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,take shelter outside the city!\NWe cannot warrant your lives if you stay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! We're going to be\Ncaught up in the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things are finally starting\Nto become hectic, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.98,0:19:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and start fighting,\Nalready, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things are so slow, I can't stand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.99,0:20:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if he is the king,\Nor if he is the king,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.66,0:20:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take guarding him for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't take it!\NCan't, can't, for crying out loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.33,0:20:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, sure, slipping\Npast the palace guards
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and kidnapping this guy is a mission\Nthat only we could carry out,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.01,0:20:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now that it's over,\Nnothing could be more boring than this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Mr. 4?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.35,0:20:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are so slow when it comes\Nto answering me, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.69,0:20:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, my back is sore!\NMy back hurts! My back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.35,0:20:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaka... Koza...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.02,0:20:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must not fight. You yourselves\Nare what this country is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.69,0:20:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must not overcome each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.03,0:20:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who lament war...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.71,0:20:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who go to war...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.99,0:21:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who incite war...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who know the truth,\Nand would prevent it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each of their feelings are at odds,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as they clash in the\Ncapital city of Alubarna.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:33.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Port town of Nanohana"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.35,0:21:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The final revolt has begun, has it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a ship.\NVivi-sama and the others
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,appear to have arrived in this land safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must hurry. I do hope I am in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.58,0:22:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always wanted to talk about it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.85,0:22:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't even say half of it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.79,0:22:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm by your side, I glitter\Nevery time we share a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.10,0:22:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The smile you gently gave me\Nwas a very happy and kind one
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.65,0:22:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glory glory you're my shine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.02,0:22:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're here, even\Nthese tears turn to courage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.56,0:22:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be strong,\NI want to share with you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.10,0:23:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I'll make it there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.31,0:23:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see it! There's Alubarna!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.98,0:23:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! Everyone ready?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.32,0:23:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rebel army is all yours, Vivi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.99,0:23:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't stop them now, then all\Nthat we've done will be for naught!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.66,0:23:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, listen to what\NI have to say, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.99,0:23:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I just heard a voice...\NAm I imagining things?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.00,0:23:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.33,0:23:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Rebel Army vs. Royal Army!\NShowdown at Alubarna!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.00,0:23:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.34,0:23:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
